Description

About Caring with Care, LLC

Caring With CARE, LLC is an in-home care agency located in Santa Clara, California, providing affordable and quality personal and respite care services for seniors and adults who require extra care. They offer a range of services such as bathing, dressing, toileting/incontinence care, meal preparation, transferring, medication reminders, and respite care to support family caregivers.

The agency is committed to treating clients with respect and dignity while promoting their physical, mental, and emotional well-being. They provide flexible scheduling options, allowing caregivers to be scheduled on an as-needed basis or a regular schedule to give families peace of mind.

Caring With CARE is BBB accredited with an A+ rating and is led by Vice President Isabel Garcia. The agency operates Monday through Friday from 8 AM to 5 PM and is located at 2086 Walsh Ave #C2, Santa Clara, CA 95050. Contact number is (408) 217-8064.

Features

Personal Care Assistance: Caregivers assist with bathing, dressing, toileting, grooming, meal preparation, transferring, and medication reminders, emphasizing dignity and respect.

Respite Care Services: Offers temporary care to relieve family caregivers, ensuring loved ones receive continuous support while family members rest or attend to other needs.

Flexible Scheduling: Provides both regular and on-demand (as-needed) care options, accommodating client routines and family schedules.

Qualified, Compassionate Caregivers: Staff members are trained to promote clients physical comfort, emotional well-being, and independence at home.

Affordable Home Care: Focuses on delivering high-quality yet cost-conscious services for seniors seeking trustworthy home assistance.

Locally Owned and Operated: Serves Santa Clara County with consideration for nearby areas upon request.

Strong Reputation: Holds an A+ rating from the Better Business Bureau since 2022, recognized for professionalism and dependable care delivery.

Positive Client Feedback: Families praise the agencys punctuality, flexibility, and the affectionate manner in which caregivers treat clients.

Family Support Focus: Aims to make in-home care an emotionally supportive experience for both clients and their families.

Convenient Payment Options: Accepts cash, checks, and Zelle payments for ease and flexibility.
